The '''Chancellor Palpatine Commercial Nexus''' was a large [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] built during, and named after, the [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|chancellorship]] of [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]. It was connected to the [[Chancellor Palpatine Spaceport]], and the combined complex dwarfed all other spaceports on Coruscant.

